Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:20.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.13,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就回來 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:31.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是真的離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我 你和夜禍之間發生了什麼對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 不要對我隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 敏感的公主也挺傷人腦筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:45.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是已經一週了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她也沒有其它的地方好去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她果然已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個毛毯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:09.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也並非就是茉莉在這裡的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能其他人睡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那茉莉到底去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想已經不在這個小鎮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她是打算在依人面前消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你們今天那麼要好一起遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼 一大早就去約會啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說一直約會到早上？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮同學好像是一個人住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到的懲罰也一個人承受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是奉獻精神呢還是專情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:17.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過的對吧 沒有在捉弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不過你還真講究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:55.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶要低溫殺菌的 豆腐要選100％國產大豆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雞蛋也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為依人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉要是能快點回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話依人也會很早回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人就能悠閒地吃飯了不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為茉莉她會回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依很希望她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為茉莉很喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她說因為這裡有藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:35.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她是這樣說的 不過我也不清楚什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概是依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓茉莉看到藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:06.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃說改變一下房間的佈置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了 依人去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 這裡的照片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:33.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是我最重要的照片啊 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:43.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:54.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請等等 蒼乃說是為了依人才改變房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:56.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說一看見就又會想起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:05.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃不想讓依人留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:06.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼回想起茉莉的事會覺得痛苦啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她出走的時候也沒有跟我們說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她也許馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:19.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她不會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人你自己也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:40.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:41.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓依人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人一定也會覺得很抱歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 突然發火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:35.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟小依說用十天的冰棒來跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等會兒你要去買給她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:40.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不好 擅自做出那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 稍微去散個步怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概也明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明白什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:11.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉會離開 不再回來的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果我真的這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:20.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就會有再也見不到她的這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會去遇見茉莉的地方 兩個人去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括這裡的教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉以前就住這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:03.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個米糠醃的黃瓜好吃死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也不用每天早上都來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是姊妹倆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:31.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不好？ 蒼乃邀請我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,聽呀 這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘訣就是糠床要好好保存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 糠床是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:48.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,能幹的女性就是在這方面做得好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那算是能幹的女性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名好幾次都做不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:57.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:02.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:06.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得約定嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,放心啦 今天下午是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:13.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:25.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:48.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:49.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 我也差不多該去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他每天都在店門口等那個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也許真的是被媽媽帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候又變成母女設定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:24.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個喜歡上鬍子帥哥的女人和他過去一定有過什麼經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後結婚 生下那個孩子後就離婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外沒有其它可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒覺得有其它可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有別的可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我聽過那個孩子談起她的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,用很可怕的表情質問鬍子帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和YACA之間發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,YACA（夜禍）？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對 是母親的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 然後就如我所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫YACA的女人還是忘不了她的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過了一個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 所以今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:13.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,特地跑到學校來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,順便來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,順便？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這副打扮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:35.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是難得出來 遇到這場大雨太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒這回事 是難得的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好天氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:14:59.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:06.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎？ 不買
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是為了買才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:26.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想看看依人經常去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想看遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下那麼大雨幾乎看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管如此 可是比起晚上能夠看得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然霧好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很美 世界有了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:07.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:14.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,綠色的草 藍色的屋頂 紅色的船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全都被染上了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:25.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚不可能看到的美麗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,上次像這樣和姊姊出來是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:33.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為姊姊一直都在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想應該很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都淋濕了 快點回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說好要去真名打工的餐廳看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說有時間的話再去的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾 毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:12.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:17.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去 不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:55.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:10.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:19.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:31.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:06.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應你 不會再次出現在你們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:41.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:57.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒有實現我們的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒有讓茉莉看到藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回去吧 好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也沒看到鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,像平時那樣的鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著憂鬱感的鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:41.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,男人味十足的鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:45.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,願明天能看到鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:17.07,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(500,500)}灰色的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:46.86,FBT,NTP,442,0,224,,揮不去的回憶
